nodes.text: An unidentified Duros lived on Void Station, working as a servant for Jib Kopatha, during the Galactic Civil War.

In 0 ABY, the Sith Lord Darth Vader arrived to Void Station, planning to extract information from the information broker. The Duros noticed Vader's Lambda-class shuttle arriving, and rushed to tell the Bothan. Kopatha didn't believe him at first, and the servant tried to convince his boss. Their conversation were interrupted when Vader entered the throne room.
